data.description: AN AMAZING deal for a very fortunate buyer.  Wrapped in welcoming allure, this Savannah Sub home radiates with thoughtful updates. Fresh wall color flows throughout an open layout featuring warm natural light from large windows throughout. A spacious two-story living area is warmed by a tiled fireplace. An open kitchen features generous cabinetry while a bright dining area features outdoor connectivity to a patio w/ a cozy firepit. Beyond, peaceful views of open space unfold inspiring a private outdoor escape. One of four sizable bedrooms, a remodeled primary suite boasts a walk-in closet and a serene bath w/ a walk-in shower and soaking tub. A versatile, upper-level loft presents space for a home office or seating area. Downstairs, a partially finished basement offers the potential for personalization w/ a living area grounded by a fireplace and plenty of flex space. Additional storage is found in a backyard shed and in a two-car attached garage. Residents enjoy a coveted location w/ close proximity to pocket parks.
